{"tid":1414862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"由放煙數字頻率反映","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:57:34.000Z","uid":262017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40e5a83d17576329b369f3194a182d93f7dc077f","tid":1414862,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:54:23.000Z","msg":"今日放煙比較多，有可能因為示威地點數見太多，狗力不足所致。<br />\n<br />\n1.狗太少，d狗自己都好緊張<br />\n2.有心部署，以武裝壓制人數不足<br />\n<br />\n正題，經過今日狗狗們必然重新調整，方法唔起到講廢事教狗，但今日既優勢將會縮短，請勿過份執著今日經驗。<br />\n而最危險最擔心係，警黑進一步合作，理用當區黑社會打壓示威者，以應對狗力不足及支援需時問題。<br />\n<br />\n北角已經出左2x件蛋散，除左人多諗唔到點應對，切勿過分分散，唔對路be water,萬事小心"},{"pid":"17834b65ded85e2a0fa3916292961c7cd4b8d48a","tid":1414862,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"自推5連"},{"pid":"1ea3ac45aa584a83633c36742ce753364d25e29a","tid":1414862,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"4推"},{"pid":"3d8255a1c4111b23c3e7921ed9fcd9f15fd3f6ee","tid":1414862,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:57:14.000Z","msg":"3推"},{"pid":"be93bc1d9c8a2e8801b2a6ec0ae834b045aa7a33","tid":1414862,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:57:24.000Z","msg":"2推"},{"pid":"c76558ec3c24a1cec4b8ee08dc062e1399d2ef47","tid":1414862,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"1推"}]}